data.title: "Artbound Presents: Studio A" Quetzal (TV Episode 2014)
data.meta_description: Quetzal: Directed by Mike Corey. With Tylana Enomoto, Quetzal Flores, Martha Gonzalez, Alberto Lopez. The Grammy-winning band Quetzal mixes sounds of traditional Mexican "son jarocho" music with a contemporary twist. Catch their lively performance on Studio A.
